* Type Mismatch\nHandling
** Pattern
***_ Separate valid from invalid
***_ Process good data first
***_ Quarantine bad records
** Valid Records
***_ Filter with try_cast IS NOT NULL
***_ INSERT INTO silver table
***_ cast() to target types
** Invalid Records
***_ Filter with try_cast IS NULL
***_ INSERT INTO quarantine table
***_ Preserve raw values
***_ Add quarantine timestamp
***_ Add reason field
** Benefits
***_ Pipeline continues running
***_ Bad data preserved for analysis
***_ No data loss
***_ Auditable quality issues
@endmindmap
